name: Shaker_Series_18-inch_Natural_Finish_5.5-inch_Deep_Inside_On_The_Wall_Cabinet
description:
Ideal as a medicine cabinet, spice cabinet, or storage cabinet anywhere the Shaker Series On The Wall cabinet is the perfect choice. This functional 18-inch cabinet mounts onto a wall with built-in cleats inside, for an easy installation.
